I move to amend the Committee Substitute for Senate Bill No. 2028 as follows:
1. On Page 3, Line 9, by striking after the semicolon, the word “and”;
2. On Page 3, Line 9 ½, by inserting a new paragraph 3 to read as follows and renumbering the
subsequent paragraph:
“3. Preclude the advertising of the sale of ungraded raw milk and raw milk products; and”;
3. On Page 3, Lines 15 and 16, by deleting SECTION 3 in its entirety and renumbering subsequent
section; and
4. By amending the title to conform.
